{"version": "0.2.0-beta.6", "title": "Shin Seiki Evangelion", "title_uuid": "cc3209cd-c119-4870-b06c-9a34f447db7e", "volume": "Shin Seiki Evangelion 5", "volume_uuid": "4aef3d00-cab7-4870-9e59-b6f13b132a55", "pages": [{"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1821, "img_height": 1504, "blocks": [{"box": [142, 487, 491, 936], "vertical": false, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["貞本義行", "つ年間大変お待たせたしました", "ついに出ました５巻！！", "まずは今、本屋でこの本買って読ん", "でくれてるあなたに心から＂ありが", "とう・。心やさしいいあなたはあえて遅", "れた理由を問いいたださず、ただただ", "６巻も気長に待ちますといってくれ", "るに違いありません。", "そう．．．きっとそうです。たぶん．．．お", "そらく．．．そうであってほしい・お願い。", "よ〜し体を鍛えて匍匐前進〜ん．．．", "って、走れよオレの"]}, {"box": [51, 1445, 312, 1463], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["カバー印刷共同印刷株式会社"]}, {"box": [316, 1448, 510, 1461], "vertical": false, "font_size": 13.0, "lines": ["装幀ノ鹿住忠広＋ＢＥ－ＥＮＴＣ"]}, {"box": [1057, 12, 1303, 39], "vertical": false, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["Ｍａｃｋｏｇｅｔｕｒｅｃｏｎｆｉｃｅｌ"]}, {"box": [1068, 49, 1314, 119], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["新聞系の"]}, {"box": [1477, 1322, 1604, 1381], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["最後、"]}, {"box": [1399, 1386, 1675, 1463], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＹｏｕＴｕｂｅＴｕｓｔｉｏｎの", "原作／ＧＡＩＮＡＸ"]}, {"box": [1721, 1009, 1818, 1412], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["『自本義行", "原作ＧＡＩＮＡＸ"]}, {"box": [1724, 1429, 1810, 1475], "vertical": false, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["ＫＣＡ１２．５", "角川書服"]}], "img_path": "img001.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1148, "img_height": 1495, "blocks": [{"box": [1051, 124, 1137, 187], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．", "．．．"]}, {"box": [349, 391, 702, 433], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["ＸａｄｏｋｅｗａＣｏｎｉｃｓＡ"]}, {"box": [212, 515, 810, 773], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["新世紀", "新世紀"]}, {"box": [1034, 224, 1140, 763], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["『エヴァンゲリオ。", "新世紀"]}, {"box": [428, 771, 617, 811], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["原作ＧＡＩＮＡＸ"]}, {"box": [354, 898, 687, 940], "vertical": false, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["ＹｏｓＨｉｖｅＲ（・ＳＡＤＡＮＯＴＯ"]}, {"box": [1045, 981, 1145, 1360], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["『貞本義行", "原作ＧＡＩＮＡＸ"]}, {"box": [1041, 1436, 1142, 1493], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＩＫＣＡＩ２．５角川書店"]}], "img_path": "img002.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [{"box": [538, 1280, 595, 1311], "vertical": false, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["漫画"]}, {"box": [609, 1181, 812, 1235], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ｖ６ｌｕｍｅｙ"]}, {"box": [874, 1177, 977, 1231], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["基礎"]}, {"box": [712, 1330, 979, 1403], "vertical": false, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["ＹＯＳＨＡＫＡＳＤＡＭＯＴＯ", "原作／ＧＡＮＩＡＸ"]}], "img_path": "img003.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [], "img_path": "img004.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [], "img_path": "img005.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [{"box": [309, 221, 729, 302], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＰＲＯＧＲＡＭ"]}, {"box": [420, 323, 630, 353], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["ＥＶＡＮＧＥＬＩＯＮ５"]}, {"box": [195, 596, 468, 662], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＡＥＥ２９基標－"]}, {"box": [190, 408, 588, 455], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＩＭＥ２７パーティー"]}, {"box": [196, 507, 654, 551], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＩＭＥ２の傷跡をたどれば、"]}, {"box": [506, 682, 653, 702], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ｈｔｈｅ．Ｇ－ｓｈｏｃｋ！"]}, {"box": [767, 424, 887, 1062], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["７３１５５８１１１３７１６１"]}, {"box": [190, 701, 743, 854], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["Ｓｎｉｓｓの受け止めろ重力攻撃！", "ＳＩＥＥＭＩ－ネルス停電"]}, {"box": [199, 887, 598, 951], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["しかし", "ＳＩＭＥ２真実の深淵"]}, {"box": [199, 1005, 561, 1047], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＩＭＥスリアクアリウム"]}, {"box": [375, 1196, 551, 1220], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["Ｎ＜ＡＦＮＳＴＭＬＪ"]}, {"box": [401, 1304, 605, 1329], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["ＩＫＡＲＩＧＥＮＤＯＨ"]}], "img_path": "img006.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [{"box": [14, 106, 44, 270], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["登場人物紹介"]}, {"box": [88, 108, 448, 324], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["本編の主人公．ＩＯ年", "以上もの間、伯父の", "家に預けられて育つ", "突然、父・ゲンドウによりネルフに呼", "ばれエウァのいイロットとなる。（１４歳"]}, {"box": [231, 336, 443, 464], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["葛城三サトネルフォ制服作戦", "ネルフ本部戦術作戦！！！"]}, {"box": [88, 534, 443, 592], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["にあたる。おおらかな性格でシンジの", "数少ない理解者花の独身．．．。〈９歳〉"]}, {"box": [88, 624, 451, 859], "vertical": false, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["シンジの実父。特務", "機関ネルフの最高言", "令長官。任務室上主", "義で実の息子にも冷徹だが、レイには", "不思議な思いやりを見せる。（４８歳）"]}, {"box": [256, 469, 443, 526], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.5, "lines": ["部作戦局第一課所属", "シンジの直属の上司"]}, {"box": [493, 246, 943, 1052], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["エヴァのパイロットとなる決意をし、ネルフと学校の新生活にもよう", "やく慣れ始めたシンジの前に、新たなチルドレンが現われた。１４歳に", "して大学を修了、卓越した判断能力と抜群の操縦センスを持つ天才美", "少女、惣流・アスカ・ラングレーがネウァ弐号機のバイロットとして", "ネルフにやってきた。最初のうちにこそ仲間が増えて喜んでいたが、ア", "スカの極端な二重人格ぶりに戸惑うシンジ。そこへ新たなる使徒が来", "襲撃、シンシとアスカで迎撃するが、コンビネーションの悪さから玉砕", "してしまう。そこでミサトが出した作戦は、二人で同じ部屋で暮らし", "完璧なユニゾンを作って最破する、というものだった。特訓を通して", "シンジはアスカの意外な一面を見て、思いを改めることに．．．"]}, {"box": [927, 282, 972, 669], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["●前巻までのあらすじ"]}, {"box": [243, 890, 388, 970], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["綾波レイ", "先生は"]}, {"box": [90, 1065, 443, 1121], "vertical": false, "font_size": 21.5, "lines": ["わたファースト・チルドレンという以", "外の経歴は不明の謎の美少女。（１４歳）"]}, {"box": [257, 967, 445, 1057], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["零号機のバイロット。", "マルドゥック機関の", "報告書によって選ば"]}, {"box": [90, 1130, 458, 1387], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["惣流・アスカ・ラングレー．．．", "ドイツから来た弐号", "機のバイロット。頭", "脱函日身体「「業績証センス抜群の完全無敵の", "バーフェクト美少女（性格）以外、１４歳"]}], "img_path": "img007.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [{"box": [624, 848, 661, 960], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["フケツ"]}], "img_path": "img008.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [{"box": [573, 81, 739, 126], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＡＧＥ．２７"]}], "img_path": "img009.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [], "img_path": "img010.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [], "img_path": "img011.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [], "img_path": "img012.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [{"box": [865, 155, 931, 279], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["やはり", "ここもか．．．"]}, {"box": [838, 535, 945, 800], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["マルドゥック機関と", "つながる１０％の企業のうち", "１０６がダミー"]}, {"box": [307, 576, 375, 723], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["マルドゥック", "機関"]}, {"box": [440, 829, 611, 1046], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["エヴァンゲリオン", "操縦者選出のために", "設けられた", "人類補完委員会", "直属の諮問機関："]}, {"box": [713, 1156, 777, 1302], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["そしてここが", "１０７コ目"]}, {"box": [135, 1182, 250, 1334], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["組織の実体は", "未だ不透明", "．．．か"]}], "img_path": "img013.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [{"box": [873, 129, 905, 229], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["しかし．．．"]}, {"box": [788, 176, 857, 395], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["組織の実権を", "裏で握っているのは"]}, {"box": [138, 170, 161, 291], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["おそらく．．．"]}], "img_path": "img014.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [{"box": [312, 608, 333, 728], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["どうする？"]}, {"box": [199, 696, 263, 843], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["明後日からの", "中間テスト"]}], "img_path": "img015.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [{"box": [829, 117, 928, 289], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["どないするか", "わかっとったら", "苦労せんわい"]}, {"box": [395, 97, 569, 330], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["碇っおまえ", "前の学校じゃ", "優等生だったんと", "ちゃうんか"]}, {"box": [81, 130, 229, 301], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["仕方ないよ", "こっち来てから", "勉強してるヒマ", "なんかないし"]}, {"box": [898, 404, 938, 464], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["僕は"]}, {"box": [615, 405, 686, 531], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["腹を", "くくるよ．．．"]}, {"box": [657, 689, 708, 790], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["賛成！！"]}, {"box": [793, 682, 925, 854], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["よ～～し", "こうなったら", "今から碇んちで", "作戦会議や"]}, {"box": [481, 680, 566, 826], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["なんで僕の", "家なんだよ"]}, {"box": [315, 691, 432, 839], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["たぶん仕事で", "まだ帰って", "ないよ"]}, {"box": [81, 923, 183, 1081], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["それでも", "待つ！！"]}, {"box": [854, 1085, 925, 1257], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["ミサトさんに", "会えるから"]}, {"box": [464, 1079, 566, 1225], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["そんな", "こったろうと", "思った．．"]}], "img_path": "img016.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [{"box": [788, 84, 903, 271], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["お邪魔", "しまー", "．．．"]}, {"box": [643, 1038, 673, 1127], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["さあ．．．"]}, {"box": [829, 1050, 951, 1254], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["なんやこの", "ダンボール箱の", "山は？"]}, {"box": [117, 1054, 235, 1225], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["さあって", "ここおまえの", "部屋だろ？"]}], "img_path": "img017.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [{"box": [887, 133, 932, 305], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["残念でしたァ"]}, {"box": [525, 628, 614, 835], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["今日からここは", "あたしの部屋よ"]}, {"box": [876, 951, 926, 1232], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["出たぁ～～～"]}, {"box": [337, 616, 444, 893], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["うわーっ"]}, {"box": [580, 967, 685, 1136], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["出たってなによ", "人をオバケ", "みたいに"]}, {"box": [211, 960, 247, 1052], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["惣流．．．"]}, {"box": [88, 1040, 161, 1184], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["なんで君が", "ここに．．．"]}], "img_path": "img018.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [{"box": [886, 120, 950, 241], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ミサトに", "誘われたの"]}, {"box": [717, 123, 813, 291], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["ほんとは", "ひとりのほうが", "気楽だけど"]}, {"box": [337, 113, 410, 263], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["僕にひと言も", "相談なく．．．？"]}, {"box": [219, 114, 254, 226], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["なによっ"]}, {"box": [103, 114, 176, 291], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["なんかモンク", "あるっての？"]}, {"box": [842, 353, 943, 525], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["ミサトが", "どうしてもって", "言うしィ"]}, {"box": [841, 580, 938, 848], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["まあんたは", "あたしのストレス解消の", "相手にぴったりだし"]}, {"box": [662, 599, 767, 746], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["たっぷり", "かわいがって", "あげるわ"]}, {"box": [120, 595, 227, 835], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["じゃあ僕のストレスは", "いったいどうしろって", "いうんだヨ？"]}, {"box": [887, 919, 950, 1068], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["あ～～あ", "それにしても"]}, {"box": [780, 921, 951, 1089], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["日本の住宅って"]}, {"box": [781, 922, 841, 1066], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["なんでこーも", "狭いのかしら"]}, {"box": [611, 913, 717, 1066], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["荷物が半分も", "入らないじゃ", "ない"]}, {"box": [363, 909, 538, 1079], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["ちょっとシンジ", "あんたの荷物", "さっさと隣の", "物置に", "運んでよね"]}, {"box": [235, 915, 273, 990], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["え？"]}, {"box": [138, 910, 183, 1059], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["わー", "っ"]}], "img_path": "img019.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [{"box": [826, 112, 938, 266], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["碇．．．", "かわいそうな", "ヤツ"]}, {"box": [622, 107, 737, 263], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["僕は", "うらやましい", "けど．．．"]}, {"box": [497, 120, 576, 239], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["はーい", "ただいま"]}, {"box": [825, 541, 933, 782], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["それぞれ勝手なこと", "言ってないで", "手伝ってくんないかな"]}, {"box": [496, 518, 577, 608], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ミサト", "さん"]}, {"box": [101, 314, 175, 461], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["仲よく", "やってるッ？"]}, {"box": [93, 532, 193, 632], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あ", "お邪魔", "してます"]}, {"box": [804, 839, 925, 1044], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ひどいですよ", "僕に何の断りも", "なく"]}, {"box": [494, 843, 610, 1018], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["こめんごめん", "急に決まった", "ことだからさ"]}, {"box": [316, 846, 447, 1049], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["アスカが自分で", "来たいって", "言ったのよ"]}, {"box": [391, 1210, 429, 1292], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["え？"]}], "img_path": "img020.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1490, "blocks": [{"box": [819, 135, 962, 355], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["シンジ君だけ", "引きとって", "彼女を断るわけにも