"いかなる", "生命の", "存在も許さない", "死の世界．．．南極か"]}], "img_path": "img111.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1495, "blocks": [{"box": [827, 113, 932, 240], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["いやこや", "地獄という", "べきかな"]}, {"box": [582, 99, 655, 294], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["だが我々人類は", "ここに立っている"]}, {"box": [173, 309, 296, 334], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["は、はい。"]}, {"box": [80, 112, 152, 257], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["生物として", "生きたままだ"]}, {"box": [814, 527, 924, 673], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["科学の力で", "守られている", "からな"]}, {"box": [78, 532, 157, 654], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["科学は人の", "力だよ"]}, {"box": [945, 798, 972, 897], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["だが碇．．．"]}, {"box": [761, 770, 899, 1027], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["その傲慢さが", "１５年前の悲劇", "セカンド・インパクトを", "引き起こしたのだ"]}, {"box": [214, 1130, 277, 1252], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["そして結果", "この有様だ"]}, {"box": [74, 1239, 170, 1363], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["与えられた", "罰にしては", "大きすぎる"]}], "img_path": "img112.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1045, "img_height": 1495, "blocks": [{"box": [866, 91, 931, 214], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["だが原罪の", "汚れなき"]}, {"box": [770, 175, 834, 297], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["浄化された", "世界だ"]}, {"box": [148, 502, 259, 671], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["報告します", "ネルフ本部より", "入電です"]}, {"box": [776, 738, 883, 886], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["３日９時", "ネルフ上空に", "使徒出現"]}, {"box": [933, 986, 954, 1066], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["．．．．．．？？"]}, {"box": [553, 969, 578, 1110], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["これで７つか"]}, {"box": [467, 975, 500, 1030], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ああ"]}, {"box": [211, 759, 356, 954], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": [